Table - Class in <Unnamed>
Table is a class which can can be used by a ToyRobot allowing it to be placed on the surface and moved around.
Table() - Constructor for class Table
Parameterless constructor which instantiates a square table 5 units high and 5 units wide.
ToyRobot - Class in <Unnamed>
ToyRobot creates a toy robot which can be placed on a Table and moved around.
ToyRobot() - Constructor for class ToyRobot
Basic constructor which creates an instance of the ToyRobot with a position of 0, 0 while facing north.
